data.title: Welcome to Darlington County, South Carolina
data.text:
Darlington County Council meetings are in person and live-streamed on Darlington County Council Live Meetings Facebook page.

To access the live stream, go to Darlington County website at www.darcosc.com, scroll to the middle of the page to Feature, and click on the live stream link or go to https://www.facebook.com/DarlingtonCountyCouncilLive

To access archived live-stream videos of County Council meetings, go to Darlington County website at www.darcosc.com. From the Government tab, click on County Council, then County Council Agendas, Minutes, & Videos. A list of the Council Meetings will appear in the center of the page. Click on More to access the meeting video, then click on the County Council Meeting Video link.

To access videos prior to 2022, from County Council webpage, click Archive of County Council Meeting Videos. The videos are listed by date.

For questions, please contact the Clerk to Council at 843-944-8270 or jbishop@darcosc.net.
